description.narrative:
The overall objective of the PAGE Programme is to contribute to the improvement of the living conditions of the populations in West Africa through strengthened policies and institutional environmental framework.
To achieve this general objective, five specific objectives were devised as follows:
SO1: To contribute to the implementation of Integrated Water Resources Management (IWRM) in the Volta, Niger, Senegal and Mono Basins;
SO2: To contribute to the mainstreaming of the environmental dimension in the management of the Volta, Niger, Senegal and Mono Basins;
 
SO3: To contribute to the sustainable management of the goods and services derived from the ecosystems in the Niger, Volta, Senegal and Mono Basins;
SO4: To contribute to the mainstreaming of climate change in national and local planning in the Niger, Volta, Senegal and Mono Basins;
SO5: To contribute to the restoration of degraded ecosystems in the Niger, Volta, Senegal and Mono Basins.
